				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Kaledin Stoneforge here... These nasty ghouls are actually not too tough.. they con blue to a 25 enchanter in my group, and every single on has conned blue to me, a level 30 paly.  In addition to the Bronze they ALWAYS seem to drop, the rare drop is 'a ghoul heart' which from what I have been told is for the new Ghoulbane quest they just implemented last patch.  I can solo these fairly easily, losing between 1 to 3 bubbles of health..  also unlike most ghouls... THEY DONT ROOT! so running is easy..  there are regular ghoul placeholders for these guys, and those are the same in every respect as the crazed, just never drop the heart...  Hope this helps...<BR>
<BR>
Kaledin Stoneforge<BR>
