				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A freind of mine told me about the new spawn so I went to go check it out with a lvl 30 ranger. Here is what I discovered:<BR>
Yes they do spawn on the cliff by the water fall and by the gazebo just as all posts have said.<BR>
They always drop a piece of small bronze armor and I usually got about 3.5pp with auto-spilt off. The cons ranged from blue to red, I am a 24th Pally.<BR>
They also seem to spawn in twos, even if we pulled one another would show up real quick.<BR>
Their place holder is A Ghoul which seems to be higher lvl than regular ghouls, some even conned red to me, a great suprise.  <BR>
Neither of the ghouls will root and BOTH will drop the Ghoul heart.  Hope I helped<BR>
Rondov Bloodstorm, 24th Dwarven Paladin, Nameless server.
